thread.title: Julianne

author: Julianne
title: Julianne
text: I ordered three large apple trees, blueberry bushes, black raspberry plants, and pawpaw trees. They arrived well wrapped in a reasonable time. They were all dormant when they arrived, so I didn't write my review right away because I wanted to see how they did once spring came. Two of the raspberry canes didn't survive, but everything else is thriving. I had no complaints and am happy with my purchase.
